WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.187
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.187 --> 00:00:03.451
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.451 --> 00:00:04.709
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:04.709 --> 00:00:06.194
Well, it's Diana and Brandon.

00:00:06.194 --> 00:00:07.828
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:07.828 --> 00:00:13.340
Truly, we're so blessed to have you all pray with us every single time we do these videos.

00:00:13.340 --> 00:00:14.983
We were so excited, Braden.

00:00:15.474 --> 00:00:30.863
We got the report and it said we're number five because of you all coming and praying with us—of the most viewed, most watched Christian channels on YouTube.

00:00:30.863 --> 00:00:33.840
Yeah, I told D, I go, "Are you kidding me?

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:34.613
Top five.

00:00:34.613 --> 00:00:36.160
We're in the top five.

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:36.719
" Praise God.

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:38.800
Oh, glory to God, ladies and gentlemen.

00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:43.080
I said, "Lord, look what you've done in just a short amount of time.

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:44.909
" He said, "Brandon, there's much more to come.

00:00:44.909 --> 00:00:47.010
There's much more to come, son.

00:00:47.010 --> 00:00:53.466
As you stay vertical, as you stay focused, as you attract to deflect, it's all about Jesus.

00:00:53.466 --> 00:01:02.640
" But in this, I want to celebrate a milestone of being in the top five most watched Christian channels on YouTube.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:03.920
Look what God did.

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:05.280
Look what God did.

00:01:09.564 --> 00:01:12.950
It just wows us.

00:01:12.950 --> 00:01:17.040
He wows us, but you all supporting it so much.

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:22.373
I think above us was Steven Furtick and T.

00:01:22.373 --> 00:01:23.200
D.

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:27.097
Jakes and another channel I've never heard of before.

00:01:30.811 --> 00:01:31.427
It's amazing because we know those people have huge channels with millions of followers.

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:35.800
And the Lord said, "It isn't about how many are following you, son.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:46.293
It's about how many are coming and watching every single day and praying.

00:01:52.520 --> 00:01:52.800
" How many are praying?

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:54.879
We've got some praying people out there.

00:01:54.879 --> 00:01:55.680
Not subscribers, prayers.

00:01:55.680 --> 00:02:00.409
Yeah, we're not looking for subscribers; we're looking for many people to enlist in the army of God.

00:02:00.409 --> 00:02:02.170
That's what we're after, and it's just exciting.

00:02:02.170 --> 00:02:03.120
Most people go, "Well, you're bragging.

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:12.800
" I know it's not about me.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:17.280
If you knew how incapable I am of doing these videos...

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.280
People say, "Well, you're good behind the camera.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:25.943
" I said, "If you knew before, I was scared spitless to come on here and talk in front of that camera.

00:02:25.943 --> 00:02:34.320
" And I told Diana, every single time we did it, we did it over and over again, practicing and just saying, "Lord, use whatever you can.

00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:37.760
If you can use anybody, Lord, you can use me.

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:40.675
" I mean, seriously, it's amazing what the Lord has done.

00:02:42.764 --> 00:02:57.310
And I'm just so thankful that you would come on and watch with us every single time we do a video, stick around, watch it, and believe in the gifting that God's put inside of me.

00:02:57.310 --> 00:02:59.120
It's just exciting.

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:04.608
So that was part of it, you know, just saying thank you.

00:03:04.608 --> 00:03:05.760
Thank you.

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:08.959
God bless every single one of you.

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:10.560
Thank you for watching.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:16.560
So, I want to talk to you all about what I saw in our last prayer video.

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:22.060
And I didn't go over this from the last one about the pews of fire.

00:03:22.410 --> 00:03:24.891
And folks, it's time to get excited.

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:32.799
The glorious church without spot or wrinkle.

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:37.369
I'm telling you, I saw wooden pews.

00:03:40.151 --> 00:03:42.000
And it was the same church the Lord showed me, and the bell towers.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:46.560
Remember He said, "I'm giving one last call.

00:03:49.131 --> 00:03:53.580
" And I saw the bells beginning to ring, one last alarm, one last call again.

00:03:53.580 --> 00:04:05.429
He showed this to me over and over again, but I saw the same church this time, and I could see through the church.

00:04:10.676 --> 00:04:13.040
And as I was looking through this beautiful church, it was in an old country area again.

00:04:14.284 --> 00:04:15.897
It was like an old Pentecostal country church in a rural area.

00:04:17.850 --> 00:04:21.440
And I could see the podium there, and there was a man of fire behind it.

00:04:21.440 --> 00:04:27.1000
Then I looked at the pews, and they were the old wooden pews made out of oak.

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:33.779
And I could see individual fires that were sitting on the pews.

00:04:33.779 --> 00:04:43.520
They were these massive fireballs, but they were small for the kids and they were large for the adults.

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:55.910
And as I looked into this church, the pews were full of fire, but each individual fire was there.

00:04:58.639 --> 00:04:58.799
And I was like, "Oh.

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:06.000
" And I wanted to stop and just look at it, but every single fire was a different color.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:23.863
There were blue fires and red fires and all kinds of really cool fires, but they were all focused at the big fire on the stage where the pastor was preaching, which caused fires in the pews.

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:29.851
The Lord said, "I want you to see what's on the front porch.

00:05:32.046 --> 00:05:43.901
" And I saw a field full of babies that were crying, and some of them had sailor outfits on—like those old baby sailor outfits with the anchor on them and the red bow tie, or a red thing around their neck.

00:05:50.319 --> 00:05:50.959
And they were all crying.

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:06.600
And the Lord spoke to me and He said, "The babies are coming.

00:06:11.627 --> 00:06:11.813
I want you to be very patient with My babies.

00:06:11.813 --> 00:06:14.693
For once, you were a baby and you needed patience.

00:06:14.693 --> 00:06:21.160
You needed to have extra care, for there are many babies that are about to come to the church.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:24.091
" He said, "Brandon, don't be hasty with them.

00:06:24.091 --> 00:06:25.577
Don't be cranky.

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:31.954
Be patient and walk in love towards them, for you were once a baby, too.

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:42.343
" And He warned me about the babies.

00:06:42.343 --> 00:06:45.200
He said, "The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:49.471
Just treat the babies that are coming with care, for there are a lot of babies.

00:06:49.471 --> 00:06:50.831
" He said, "Disciple them.

00:06:50.831 --> 00:06:53.724
Disciple the babies, for there's going to be a lot of them.

00:06:58.489 --> 00:06:58.880
Don't be mean to them.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:06:59.839
Be patient.

00:07:07.051 --> 00:07:07.314
" And I saw elderly women—which I know this was not all elderly women—but they had the old '50s clothes on, they had the old '50s hair.

00:07:07.314 --> 00:07:09.457
They looked like Leave It to Beaver moms.

00:07:09.457 --> 00:07:09.919
Wow.

00:07:10.799 --> 00:07:15.440
And they were taking care of the babies dressed up like little Leave It to Beavers.

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:21.009
Now, I thought that was interesting because it was like an old '50s style in this vision.

00:07:21.009 --> 00:07:27.430
But I saw their hair was all that old '50s hair with the old '50s clothes.

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:40.800
And they were loving on these babies outside, and they were like mothers.

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:49.810
And the Lord showed me, "There'll be many mothers that are there to help love these new babies, for you'll have to be like a mother to them.

00:08:00.399 --> 00:08:03.302
" And I saw spiritual mothers rising up, spiritual parents to help take care of these babies, because you need a Leave It to Beaver mama to nurture them, a nurturing mother.

00:08:10.212 --> 00:08:10.879
I thought it was interesting because that's the '50s mom, like Leave It to Beaver kind of people, or those old '50s shows.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:21.351
But it's just amazing because that's the way the Lord was painting this to me: we must take care of these babies and disciple them.

00:08:21.351 --> 00:08:27.707
So that was part of the vision that I saw, and the storm going on outside.

00:08:32.514 --> 00:08:34.879
The babies were crying, and God said, "Bring them in and just love on them.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:51.120
" And so, it really blessed me, and that's why I kept that out.

00:08:53.714 --> 00:09:02.346
The Holy Spirit—I told Braden, I said, "That needs to be at the front of the video, what the Lord was telling us about the babies that are coming, because it doesn't need to be buried.

00:09:02.346 --> 00:09:15.706
" There are a lot of times there's so much there that the Lord is giving us that it's an hour-long video, and there are a lot of you who don't hear that part, but this was so important that we set this apart.

00:09:15.706 --> 00:09:21.830
Another part of the vision that I saw in the previous video, I saw massive boat anchor chains.

00:09:21.830 --> 00:09:25.610
They were huge, like you would see on a massive ship.

00:09:25.610 --> 00:09:40.503
They were thick, thick chains, and they were stretching clear into the soil of the earth in Tulsa, and they were going straight up into heaven.

00:09:40.503 --> 00:09:48.811
But there was no end to the chain; I couldn't see where it ended, and I couldn't see where it began.

00:09:48.811 --> 00:09:54.320
Both ends were pulled so tight in the vision, but there was a chain in Tulsa.

00:09:57.460 --> 00:09:59.819
I saw one in the Branson area, I saw one in the Kansas City area, and I saw one in Fort Worth.

00:09:59.819 --> 00:10:05.851
And these chains were pulled tight, and they were pulling the earth, but the chains were gold, like a transparent gold.

00:10:09.464 --> 00:10:10.783
This beautiful gold, like you've never seen before—maybe in a cartoon, but never in real life.

00:10:10.783 --> 00:10:12.346
This was the most beautiful gold.

00:10:12.346 --> 00:10:24.194
But the gold was sparkling with the glory and it was being pulled, and you could actually see the torque from the earth pulling up like when you're pulling something out of the earth, like tree roots or something.

00:10:37.490 --> 00:10:37.760
You could see the dirt being pulled up on the sides of this massive chain, and it was going straight into the heavens.

00:10:47.160 --> 00:10:47.360
And I could see the grass, and I could see the dirt, and all of the stress of the earth where it was being pulled.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:54.270
Now, I don't know what that means, but I believe it has something to do with the end-time glory.

00:11:07.119 --> 00:11:07.359
And there was a pull there.

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:17.100
And I kept hearing Jacob's ladder and portals of glory pulled tight, with no slack in the chain at all—portals of glory.

00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:32.800
And I'm telling you, when the Lord showed me again about the major revival that's about to take place in Branson, Missouri, Tulsa, and Fort Worth, Texas, and all these areas—those are just some of the areas that the Lord is showing me.

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:35.600
It doesn't mean those are the only areas.

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:46.649
I want to let you know there's going to be many places where the outpouring is going to be, but this is where the Lord showed me at this particular time.

00:11:46.649 --> 00:11:52.114
So, I just thought it was amazing what the Lord was showing me about this.

00:11:52.114 --> 00:12:00.640
So, now, after I go over all those things and I saw the glory—I saw the fall time again, I keep seeing the fall.

00:12:00.640 --> 00:12:02.440
There's something about the fall.

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:04.040
It's time to rest it all.

00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:05.564
There's going to be an outpouring.

00:12:05.564 --> 00:12:07.480
There are things starting to kick off, folks.

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:12.320
When we go into this Rosh Hashanah, this major holy day, a transfer, there's something happening.

00:12:21.120 --> 00:12:21.406
He started talking to me about being ankle deep, knee deep, waist deep, over the head.

00:12:26.102 --> 00:12:28.023
And I'm telling you, folks, what we're about to see, we're not even—we're just barely in the shadow.

00:12:28.023 --> 00:12:30.519
We're just at the shallows of it.

00:12:30.519 --> 00:12:32.399
We just slipped our feet in there.

00:12:32.399 --> 00:12:34.429
We're just kind of tiptoeing around.

00:12:34.429 --> 00:12:39.460
We got our toes in there, and we're like splashing around with our Holy Ghost toes.

00:12:39.460 --> 00:12:47.960
But what God's about to do, we're going to go clear to the bottom of the massive well that He has for us with no limitation.

00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:48.540
Yes.

00:12:48.540 --> 00:12:53.257
There's no limitation for what the Lord has in store for us.

00:12:56.440 --> 00:12:58.666
And I'm telling you, it's time to believe God like you've never believed Him before.

00:13:08.868 --> 00:13:09.062
For there's Holy Ghost fire in the pews, and I'm telling you all, it's all hands on deck.

00:13:09.062 --> 00:13:12.576
'All ye that are heavy laden, I will give you rest.

00:13:12.576 --> 00:13:13.707
' Who's hungry?

00:13:13.707 --> 00:13:15.680
Who's thirsty for the next outpouring?

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:21.130
And I'm telling you, folks, He's just looking for a yielded one to say, 'Father, here am I, send me.

00:13:21.130 --> 00:13:28.080
' There's no one going to be any greater than—well, you know, He's branding this.

00:13:35.839 --> 00:13:36.079
I'm telling you, folks, it's not about platform.

00:13:42.399 --> 00:13:42.639
It's about yieldedness.

00:13:42.639 --> 00:13:43.600
It's about obedience.

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:49.200
He said, 'Brandon, I'm looking for the people who think they have such big platforms.

00:13:49.200 --> 00:13:57.120
' He said, 'The reason why they've stayed there so long and they've not increased in the glory is because I look at the heart of obedience.

00:14:01.617 --> 00:14:06.480
I reward the obedient, just like you do when your child is obedient and they are good kids and they do what you tell them to do.

00:14:11.222 --> 00:14:11.485
You say, "Pull out the trash, do these things," and then they do things without you even asking.

00:14:13.760 --> 00:14:14.503
You're like, "Oh, buddy, you're going to get blessed today.

00:14:25.336 --> 00:14:25.805
I want to take you to go get an ice cream or something fun.

00:14:25.805 --> 00:14:31.893
" You know, you just want to reward your kids.

00:14:31.893 --> 00:14:35.211
' And God is a God of rewards.

00:14:45.949 --> 00:14:47.239
And He is going to abundantly supply in these last days, not just finances, but ladies and gentlemen, He's going to pour out His Spirit upon all flesh.

00:14:57.573 --> 00:14:57.787
And you're going to see some of the greatest things you've ever seen.

00:15:14.991 --> 00:15:15.583
It's going to be, you know, from what I've seen coming.

00:15:22.509 --> 00:15:24.740
And I keep saying that over and over, but I keep getting glimpses of it when I'm praying.

00:15:31.896 --> 00:15:32.399
And the Lord keeps telling me, 'Brandon, do you understand?

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:35.668
It's more than just the finances.

00:15:35.668 --> 00:15:36.834
It's more.

00:15:36.834 --> 00:15:39.379
It's the whole man: spirit, soul, and body.

00:15:39.379 --> 00:15:45.320
' Just like Oral Roberts says, 'I'm here to minister to the whole man: spirit, soul, and body.

00:15:45.320 --> 00:15:49.750
' He wants us free in every area of our life.

00:15:49.750 --> 00:15:55.840
Not, 'Well, you know, you've got money, but you're depressed,' or, 'Well, you're whole, but you're broke.

00:15:55.840 --> 00:16:05.040
I don't have any sickness in my body, and I'm thankful for it, Lord, but you're broke.

00:16:05.040 --> 00:16:14.659
' He's like, 'I want to do over and above all that you dare ask or think according to the power that worketh in you.

00:16:14.659 --> 00:16:16.826
' What do you believe Me for?

00:16:16.826 --> 00:16:18.742
Will you believe Me for big today?

00:16:18.742 --> 00:16:20.366
Will you believe Me for the impossible?

00:16:20.366 --> 00:16:21.931
What was impossible will become possible.

00:16:21.931 --> 00:16:37.120
I'm going to take what you thought would be something that you'd be bound by your whole life, and it's going to be set-free time.

00:16:37.120 --> 00:16:44.377
I'm telling you, there's an expiration date to everything you're believing for.

00:16:47.850 --> 00:16:48.160
And it's time to believe God for big in these last days.

00:16:48.160 --> 00:16:54.000
Yes, I say a lot of heavy words, and I tell you a lot of warnings, and that's where I'm going next.

00:16:59.660 --> 00:17:01.619
But I wanted to give you something good to munch on while you're about to eat something a little sour because of what He showed me.

00:17:01.619 --> 00:17:12.491
But I just have to tell you, I tell you everything, and I'm just bold about it.

00:17:12.491 --> 00:17:14.799
But I'm not worried about it.

00:17:14.799 --> 00:17:18.130
I'm looking up, for my redemption draws nigh.

00:17:18.130 --> 00:17:27.387
But I want to tell you, there are hard times ahead for some folks because they're not looking.

00:17:27.387 --> 00:17:31.840
Now, let's go into praying over Don Jr.

00:17:31.840 --> 00:17:34.491
, okay, and all that the Lord showed us.

00:17:34.491 --> 00:17:41.280
So, the Lord showed me the White House, and I could see demonic witchcraft all over Washington, D.

00:17:41.280 --> 00:17:43.840
C.

00:17:44.853 --> 00:17:50.617
—a heavy, thick witchcraft trying to settle in over the White House, over President Trump's health.

00:18:04.444 --> 00:18:14.800
We must pray for President Trump's health, for I saw an attack trying to give him a stroke because of all the pressure, all the demonic worry, and all the stress trying to affect his immune system, trying to affect him with so much stress that he would have a heart attack or a stroke.

00:18:15.220 --> 00:18:28.240
And the Lord said, 'Pray over his heart for the circulation of the blood flowing through his veins, for there's an attack against his veins.

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:37.188
' And I saw his arteries in his neck and in his head trying to affect him, to take him out through demonic pressure.

00:18:37.188 --> 00:18:39.222
It's heavy, this Antichrist agenda.

00:18:39.222 --> 00:18:49.940
So I saw it all swirling above the White House, and it looked like the clouds in a portal turning like a hurricane above it.

00:18:49.940 --> 00:19:03.420
There were purples and blacks and dark colors that were circling like a hurricane above, and it was turning and turning all above.

00:19:03.420 --> 00:19:07.511
And I could see it; it stretched clear into the Atlantic Ocean.

00:19:07.511 --> 00:19:17.200
And I could see it over the Capitol; I could see it over where Congress, the judges, and all of it was.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:21.493
It was trying to come in over Washington, D.

00:19:21.493 --> 00:19:22.080
C.

00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:31.590
But inside of the White House were these lights, and there was light inside the home, and it looked like there was peace inside the house.

00:19:31.590 --> 00:19:35.840
As there was a storm brewing outside, there was light on the inside.

00:19:35.840 --> 00:19:37.799
And the Lord said, 'Focus on the light.

00:19:37.799 --> 00:19:38.971
Look at the light, son.

00:19:38.971 --> 00:19:41.138
' And I could see a light inside the White House.

00:19:41.138 --> 00:19:47.329
There was a storm brewing on the outside, but there was light on the inside.

00:19:56.240 --> 00:19:56.526
And the Lord said, 'Pray for him more.

00:19:56.526 --> 00:20:04.924
' Then I saw, Qasem Soleimani, I saw generals on oil-based paintings and frames that were really beautiful frames.

00:20:04.924 --> 00:20:18.177
But as—and I'll describe this as, if you remember the movie Back to the Future, as he was making the decision and he was singing on the stage and he was playing Johnny B.

00:20:18.177 --> 00:20:22.000
Goode and his brothers and sisters on the photo were fading away.

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:24.427
Remember how they were fading away?

00:20:24.427 --> 00:20:29.493
If you've watched the movie—I know it's an old movie—but it was fading away.

00:20:33.460 --> 00:20:33.840
And this is the way these photos looked.

00:20:33.840 --> 00:20:45.808
I could see these Iranian generals and they were fading away, and below this picture was fire, and it was consuming.

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:57.379
And I said, "They're in hell," and I could see the fire burning these men, for they looked like spirits.

00:20:57.379 --> 00:21:04.891
They looked like ghosts, and as the fire was burning the pictures, they said, "We want revenge.

00:21:04.891 --> 00:21:06.540
We want revenge.

00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:14.719
" And I saw their generals in a line in the photos, and they were burning.

00:21:15.119 --> 00:21:18.640
And in the photos, these people were fading away, and they were burning in hell.

00:21:23.529 --> 00:21:24.019
And the Lord showed me Don Jr.

00:21:31.380 --> 00:21:31.560
, and he became a photo, and the fire was trying to eat him.

00:21:31.560 --> 00:21:34.704
And the Lord said, "You must intercede for Don Jr.

00:21:34.704 --> 00:21:38.720
, for there's an attempt coming on his life.

00:21:39.560 --> 00:21:41.660
" I want to say this again.

00:21:57.039 --> 00:21:57.399
You must intercede for Don Jr.

00:21:57.399 --> 00:22:01.120
, for there is an attempt coming on his life.

00:22:01.120 --> 00:22:09.147
For they say, "If we cannot get to Trump, we will take out his son in revenge of what he did to our generals.

00:22:09.147 --> 00:22:13.084
" So I saw a plan and a plot to shoot and assassinate Don Jr.

00:22:14.293 --> 00:22:14.596
to take him out.

00:22:19.140 --> 00:22:19.440
